David CAIN, Jr., petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 12-9125. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, 671 F.3d 271 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied. Justice SOTOMAYOR took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
